    "sections": [
      {
        "title": "Occupation",
        "content": "2010-now. Independent consultant/advisor/trainer in image solution for VTVs, VTC-Intecom, VinEdu/Mation/Retail, TienphongBank, Hyperlogy, Niteco, Victorymedia.\n2010-now: Assuming the title of Academic Head at FPT-Arena\n2012: Guest lecturer at the London College for Fashion Studies and Keuka Program - ISVNU;\n2008-2010: Founding lecturer at Omega - the first experimental school for design in Hanoi."
      },
      {
        "title": "Logo & branding",
        "content": "One of very few designers who directs logo design at both best cost saving in production/application and catching customers at highest effectiveness based on modern material visual method.\nPrioritize the importance of key visual systematically, which helps strangly recognizing the brand even without the logo.\nExtensive art/culture foundation is a big advantage in high-class and not-easy-to-do logos."
      },
      {
        "title": "Arts & Design",
        "content": "2014-2018: Top 1% badges and top 5% most viewed portfolios on CGSociety - one of the most professional world-class computer art communities.\n2014: Winner in Graphics and Visual Communication Design Category - \"A' Prime\" International Design Award - Como Italy."
      }
    ]
